metadata.name: MIRACLE
metadata.description:
A remote and inaccessible temple and a portal to other dimensions. Here live some monks, immortal guardians, who patiently await the miracle.

This image was awarded "BEST OF THE MONTH_1ST PLACE" IN JUNE 2021 by D2 Conferences Collective.

5669X7086 px
